This report is the last ditch effort to get countries and govts to finally wake up. We are in an emergency - a full blown crisis. 

@cop26uk will likely be our last chance to convince countries to take action proportionate to the scale of this crisis. Don’t forget to let your leaders know you care! 

Speaking of @cop26uk - head to the link in our bio to donate to @toritsui_ and @uniteforclimateaction campaign to get Latin American and Caribbean activists to @cop26uk in October. ✊
